Welcome to Technicity! Before you begin, here is everything you need to know to get started.
Learn how to navigate and interact with tools and the virtual environment.
Complete the tutorial by following the checklist. This will serve as a guide for your journey in mastering electrical installation and maintenance!

First, try to grab the Hammer by pressing the Grip.
